Cards.CardDesc: A white goat that has inhabited the forest for ages. The creature is actually an elder of the woods.
A rare scarlet scorpion that can be found in the tundra -- not in the desert.

Cards.CardDesc: A monster turtle with a crimson shell. It feeds on fire.
